OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FResearch by ITV's Tonight programme
OL,6,Fhas shown that air fryer users could
OL,7,Funknowingly be putting themselves at
OL,8,Frisk.
OL,10,FFire services across the UK have
OL,11,Frevealed that emergency callouts for
OL,12,Fair fryer "user error" are nearly
OL,13,Fthree times higher than those for
OL,14,Ffaulty appliances.
OL,16,FFreedom of Information requests* have
OL,17,Fhighlighted almost 750 air fryer fires
OL,18,Fsince 2022, with the majority
OL,19,Fresulting from avoidable mistakes.
