OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FOne of the leading fire causes was
OL,6,Fusers placing their appliance on top
OL,7,Fof a conventional hob.
OL,9,FIt is thought that people who are
OL,10,Ftight for kitchen space are putting
OL,11,Fthem on top of their cookers.
OL,13,F"Air fryers are often made of plastic,
OL,14,Fwhich will burn with quite toxic
OL,15,Fsmoke," says Natasha Neale from
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Fire and Rescue
OL,17,FService.
