OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,F"They are sited in a kitchen where
OL,6,Fthere's potentially lots of other
OL,7,Fflammable items which can increase the
OL,8,Frisk".
OL,10,FKristina Owen came home to find her
OL,11,Fhouse on fire. She tells Chris Choi
OL,12,Fthat, despite not being in use, her
OL,13,Fair fryer destroyed her home
OL,15,FDuring his research, ITV News Consumer
OL,16,FEditor Chris Choi also found that
OL,17,Fanother dangerous trend is so-called
OL,18,F'cleaning hacks'.
