OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FThe misguided advice tells people that
OL,6,Fan easy way to clean their appliance
OL,7,Fis to fill it with soapy water and
OL,8,Fthen turn it on.
OL,10,FFire and Rescue Services in
OL,11,FBournemouth attended a ferocious fire
OL,12,Fin student accommodation after
OL,13,Fsomebody followed the advice.
OL,15,FAfter watching an example online, Marc
OL,16,FBarrett of Dorset & Wiltshire Fire and
OL,17,FRescue tells Chris Choi, "It's got
OL,18,Fover four million views, which is
OL,19,Fworrying.
