OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,F"We spoke to one of the students, and
OL,6,Fwhat they had done is actually fill
OL,7,Fthe air fryer with lots of water and
OL,8,FFairy Liquid, close the lid and put it
OL,9,Fon".
OL,11,FResearch featured on the programme
OL,12,Fshows that just over half of air fryer
OL,13,Fusers surveyed do not regularly clean
OL,14,Ftheir appliance.
