OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FPeople have also been putting things
OL,6,Fin their air fryer that create
OL,7,Fdangerous situations, such as tinfoil,
OL,8,Ffrayed cooking paper that isn't
OL,9,Fproperly weighed down, too much oil
OL,10,Fand over-filling food - all of which
OL,11,Fconcern fire crews.
OL,13,FExperts have said that appliances are
OL,14,Fsafe if used correctly and that they
OL,15,Fhave been tested to a standard and
OL,16,Fmade by a proper manufacturer.
