OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FAs part of their investigation, the
OL,6,FTonight programme spoke to trading
OL,7,Fstandards who work at the Port of
OL,8,FFelixstowe, where just over 2,000
OL,9,Funsafe air fryers have been seized in
OL,10,Fthe past two and a half years.
OL,12,FMany of the devices staff found had
OL,13,Ffaulty plugs or lacked proper safety
OL,14,Fmarkings and a traceable manufacturer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
