OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FClare Davies from Suffolk Trading
OL,6,FStandards said: "You might think
OL,7,Fyou're saving money, and at the time
OL,8,Fit seems like a bargain. You might
OL,9,Fsave quite a few pounds by buying
OL,10,Fcheaply online - but you've got to ask
OL,11,Fyourself, is this worth the risk of a
OL,12,Fhouse fire?"
OL,14,FInsurance provider Aviva understands
OL,15,Fthat around 70% of UK adults have an
OL,16,Fair fryer, and around 60% of people
OL,17,Fwho use them have never read the
OL,18,Finstruction manual.
