OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,FFires involving them have led to
OL,6,Fclaims averaging around #29,000, with
OL,7,Fone claim reported to have been over
OL,8,F#200,000.
OL,10,FAir fryer do's and don'ts from
OL,11,FElectrical Safety First engineer
OL,12,FGiuseppe Capanna
OL,14,F"Air fryers can be a convenient and
OL,15,Fefficient way to cook, but like any
OL,16,Felectrical appliance, they need to be
OL,17,Fused safely," Giuseppe Capanna,
OL,18,Fproduct safety engineer at Electrical
OL,19,FSafety First, said.
