OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,F"Keep the power cord away from hot
OL,6,Fareas, unplug it from the socket when
OL,7,Fnot in use and always plug it into a
OL,8,Fwall socket rather than an extension
OL,9,Flead, which can easily become
OL,10,Foverloaded if multiple high-powered
OL,11,Fappliances are connected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
