OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,F"When using your air fryer, it's best
OL,6,Fnot to leave it unattended. If you
OL,7,Fsmell burning plastic or hear any
OL,8,Funusual noises coming from your
OL,9,Fmachine, unplug it straight away and
OL,10,Fcontact the manufacturer. Avoid using
OL,11,Ftoo much oil and don't use baking
OL,12,Fpaper inside as this can both prevent
OL,13,Fthe air from circulating inside your
OL,14,Fdevice and, if not weighted down
OL,15,Fproperly, can come loose, risking
OL,16,Fcoming into contact with the heating
OL,17,Felement and catching fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
