OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,F"Different air fryers will have
OL,6,Fguidance on how much food a basket can
OL,7,Fhold, so be sure not to overfill your
OL,8,Fbasket, which can risk food coming
OL,9,Finto contact with the heating element
OL,10,Fand catching alight.
OL,12,F"Once you've finished cooking, allow
OL,13,Fit to cool down before cleaning to
OL,14,Favoid burns, and wash the basket after
OL,15,Feach use to prevent a build-up of oils
OL,16,Fand grease. Air fryers are a hugely
OL,17,Fpopular modern-day kitchen gadget,
OL,18,Fwhich many of us love and regular
OL,19,Fcleaning and proper use will help keep
OL,20,Fyour air fryer working safely and
OL,21,Fefficiently."
