OL,3,CAir fryers - Do you know the dangers?
OL,5,F Read the manufacturer's instructions
OL,6,F- not all air fryers are the same
OL,8,F Unplug when not in use
OL,10,F Use on a clean hard surface, away
OL,11,Ffrom the wall, not under cupboards and
OL,12,Faway from flammable objects
OL,14,F Keep your air fryer clean - wash the
OL,15,Fbasket after every use to avoid
OL,16,Fbuildup of oils and grease
OL,18,F Plug directly into the wall socket
OL,20,F Only use a small amount of oil, as
OL,21,Fnot much is needed
